The reason for this is that, distros change things, for example `yum` -> `dnf` and now it seems Ubuntu is changing `apt-get` -> `apt` ? it makes it easy to change these instructions (It does not depend on the dlib release cycle). Rather than keep track of these in code, it would be easier to keep track of this in documentation.

